measurements.description: Thirty-five slightly cupped flowers and one bud on three up to 56-cm inflorescences; sepals and petals apricot yellow, heavily blushed rose, striped darker rose; lip white, midline maroon stripe, maroon spots on edges, side lobes blushed yellow apically, keel yellow, speckled rose; column apricot yellow, speckled rose, anther cap white; substance firm; texture matte.
